<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>MARVELOUS LOVE OF JESUS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Van chung-sang taka Lal Isu,
 Lungkham gimthei nawpna Lalpa;
 Khawvel lei gimum cheng thuokin,
 Keidi'n Krista Na hung vakvai.

[V2]
 A mak na e! A mak na e!
 Nei lungsietna a mak taluo'i;
 Keidi'n Na thuokna Kalvari,
 Ka genthei puoi, Aw Lal Isu.

[V3]
 2. Ka genthiem thei puoi Aw Lalpa,
 Ka hun ngaih hai theilo Lalpa;
 Ka lunggil thim hun salhvak in,
 Lungsietna thieng ei muh sakin.

[V4]
 3. Lungkham buoina luipi lien hi,
 Ka pal ngam puoi Aw Hukdampa;
 Mahleh lungsietna melhawih chun,
 Keidi'n Krista Na hungkum tai.

[V5]
 4. Kengbaite kengin a chieh tau,
 Pha'kte hih thientho in a um;
 Piensuol te'n pienthakna a nei,
 Mithite kaihthawh in a um.

[V6]
 5. Khawvel ah kipahna umlo,
 Kap leh lungkham in ka um hi;
 Lungsietna Thagau thiengtho in,
 Khawvel lei dahum hih nuom hen.

[V7]
 Na lungsiet na pak tan ingka,
 Ka thachau hihhat zel inla;
 Khawvel buoina' ka len sung hin,
 Lautha'n naubang ei pui zelin.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>76</hymn_number>
</song>